Part 1 – Matka Trip 🏡✨

The past few weeks have been nothing short of bliss. We finally went home and spent some much-needed time with family. And let’s be honest—no  summer vacation ever feels complete without a trip to Naani house! So, following that beautiful tradition, we made our way there too.

What made it even more special? Watching Vamika and Parv bond like two little besties! 🥹💛 With two little ones in the family now, it was pure joy seeing their sweet sibling vibes—fighting one moment, hugging the next. That’s the magic of family… we grow together, laugh together, and vacation together 💫

Already missing my little princess so much. Love you tons 😍 Come  soon… Maasi is waiting! 🫶

PS: Stay tuned for our crazy sasural trip up next 😜🎒
